item.title: WAGMI comics
item.author: han@console.so (Han Ngo)
item.description: WAGMI is a super fun webcomic all about money stuff. We make cool and funny comics with our friends neko and mochi to help everyone with life’s wild moments. WAGMI is a super fun webcomic all about money stuff. We make cool and funny comics with our friends neko and experiments/mochi to help everyone with life’s wild moments. Check the comics: wagmicomics.com Facebook: facebook.com/wagmicomics RSS: wagmicomics.com/rss.xml Why WAGMI? After crafting tons of finance stuff and vibing with peeps from all walks of life, it hit us – it’s not just the young guns, but the adulting crew too, who need to level up their money smarts.
